This is a placeholder for a demo video file.
In a real deployment, this would be an actual MP4 video file showing Disney Solitaire gameplay.

To add a real video:
1. Replace this file with an actual demo-video.mp4
2. Or place your video at: /public/imgs/disney/demo-video.mp4
3. Common video formats: MP4, WebM, OGG

Recommended video specs:
- Resolution: 1920x1080 or 1280x720
- Duration: 30-60 seconds
- File size: Under 10MB
- Format: H.264 MP4 with AAC audio
- Bitrate: 2-5 Mbps for HD content

The video component will automatically fall back to this file if YouTube videos fail to load.